Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,not the linear domain but what it means\Nto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a million dollars? It's what it\Nmeans to you. If I stack a million
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,dollars here, it's just a bunch of\Npaper. It's a nuisance. It' be right in
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the way, wouldn't it? I'd be moving a\Nmillion dollars all the time. She I
