Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning which is in the nonlinear\Ndomain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Significance and meaning are\Nconveyed by a a flick of the eyebrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're out someplace in public and your\Nfather flicks his eyebrow. Wham! That
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,totally changed your life right that\Ninstant. Nothing was said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You get the meaning of that. Keep that\Nup and you're going to hear about it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,when you get home, young man.\NSo, the significance then, meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,value, all the things that we live for\Nand motivate all of life are all in the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,nonlinear domain.\NThey may find expression in the linear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,domain. A new um MercedesBenz\Nis in the linear domain, but it's what
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it means to you. So\Nreality then is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:18:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,what we have agreed reality is\Nthe linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But the linear is always subjectively\Nexperienced by consciousness which is in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the nonlinear.\NTherefore, the radical materialist is up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,against the absurdity\Nthat if only an objective,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,scientifically measurable\Nkind of a world is objective and true
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and verifiable, then by what right does\Nhe say so? Because that is a subjective
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,conclusion.\NSo the objective world, it doesn't even
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,exist except that it is experienced\Nsubjectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the subjective reality that we're\Ntalking about in spiritual
