Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:19:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,track the evolution of consciousness\Nthroughout all of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout the universe expressing\Nitself as this universe, this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the evolution of life on this on this\Nplanet from the beginning up till the
