Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, all such things are simple\Nwhen you see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when you see them, they're all quite\Nsimple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The mystic then the mystic is one who\Nrealizes the presence of God as
