Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go to the zoo and watch Monkey\NIsland, there is your ego right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're grasping. They're challenging\Neach other. They're bearing their teeth.
