Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.44,0:22:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't see this morning's\Nheadline, but I'm sure it's right from
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the latest review from Monkey Island\Ncalled This Planet. You have a monkey
