Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of the animal within us of course the\Nanimal the animal within us is still
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,present anatomically as the animal\Nbrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So being a human being is a very\Ndifficult thing. My uh if I was St.
