Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.64,0:50:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer matters whether it does or it\Ndoesn't. So the fallacy of criticizing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.24,0:50:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that spiritual work did not lead to the\Nhealing of something means that the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.64,0:50:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,person did not evolve you know with\Ngreat intensity you follow the course of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.55,0:50:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,miracles let's say with great intensity\Nor even aa even the 12step you take
