Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.59,0:50:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you finally reach a state whether\Nwhether whether the physicality survives
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.76,0:50:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,or not is totally irrelevant\NBecause when you totally surrender your
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.24,0:50:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,will to God, the cra the craving for\Ncontinued physicality disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.48,0:50:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And whether this physicality survives or\Nnot is frankly of no interest
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.28,0:51:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,whatsoever.\NSo a person who intensely does spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.68,0:51:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,work will either recover from the\Nphysical illness or they will reach such
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.92,0:51:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,an advanced state of consciousness that\Nwhether the body survives or not is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.00,0:51:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,really not of any particular interest.\NIt'll even reach a point where if it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.20,0:51:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,would leave soon that would be fine.\NSo spiritual endeavor then does
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.88,0:51:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,handle any and all physical illnesses.\NAnybody who's been around in any of the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.48,0:51:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness\Num
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.07,0:51:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,teachings that are prevalent of course\Nof miracles is the one I was familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.59,0:51:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,with. Uh we saw people with every\Nillness uh on the face of the earth go
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.55,0:51:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,into remission and recover.\NAnd that started these attitudinal
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.88,0:51:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,healing centers which were based on\Nuh a group um spiritual approach to
