Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.35,0:52:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,every kind of illness known to mankind\Nremitt.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.40,0:52:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And this particular body which I was\Nafflicted with all kinds of disasters
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.20,0:52:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in my in the late 30 my when my 30some\Nrather was slowly remitted from a whole
