Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.68,0:55:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that, I would always be able to see just\Nwhat I needed to see, the pedestrian
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.16,0:55:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,right before\NI ran over it, so I missed it. The stop
