Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.11,0:55:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hairy. But um so anyway, this six\Nsix weeks I surrendered surrendered my
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.40,0:56:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,survival to the presence of God.\NAnd um the infinite president uh guided
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.40,0:56:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,everything which it has since 1965.\NAnyway, the illusion that the the the
