Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.40,0:56:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,actually it's because of the self with a\Ncapital S that you survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.79,0:56:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly was not the ego keeping me\Nalive. So anyway, I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.40,0:56:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I guess you never get to see\Nanything again. I mean, I couldn't see
