Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.04,0:56:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't see anything far.\NYou can't see either close or far, then
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.68,0:56:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't see anything, can you? So, uh,\NI knew, you know, so I knew it was light
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.44,0:56:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,or dark. But so one day I was standing\Nin the kitchen of a friend uh and I
