Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.79,0:58:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,discomforts.\NSo we'll try to recontextualize all
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.72,0:59:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,these things as\Nthe the nerv physiology of the nervous
