Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.44,1:03:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,take a break now. We'll take we'll start\Nthe next session with some questions and
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.68,1:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,go where this audience uh would like to\Ngo. We've covered a great variety of
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.92,1:04:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,subjects and any one of them is a\Ntickoff point from which one question
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.92,1:04:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,can keep me going for an hour\Nwhich I promise not to do. First we ask
